Class AslTreeAdaptor

  • java.lang.Object

        • interp.AslTreeAdaptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.antlr.runtime.tree.TreeAdaptor

    public class AslTreeAdaptor
extends org.antlr.runtime.tree.CommonTreeAdaptor
    This is the tree adaptor for the extended class of AST nodes. It re-defines some required methods to cast the AST tree nodes to the new AST nodes.
